name: Gamebanana Miku Mods
short: A cog that searches for Hatsune Miku: Project DIVA Mega Mix+ mods on Gamebanana
description: This cog allows users to search for mods for the game Hatsune Miku: Project DIVA Mega Mix+ on the Gamebanana website. Users can search for mods by name or by category, and the cog will return a list of matching mods with links to their Gamebanana pages.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any user data persistently.
install_msg:
Thanks for installing Gamebanana Miku Mods!
Please report any bugs/log output in *#support_other-cogs* on the cog support server (https://discord.gg/GET4DVk).
author: crayyy_zee
